Tx

Tx: { address?: undefined | string; chain: Bitcoin | Zcash | BitcoinCash; utxo?: UTXO } | { chain: Ethereum; hash: string }
  • Defined in utxo.ts:27

Tx refers to an Ethereum transaction and its hash, or a BTC/ZEC/BCH UTXO. RenVM only returns the address when releasing funds in response to a burn, so a Tx may include an address instead of a UTXO.
